Type Casting - converting value of one type to another

2 types: widening/implicit/automatic
        narrowing/explicit/manual

Conditional Statements:
1. if statement
2. switch statement

if statement:

SYNTAX:
    if (condition) {
          code A;
    }
    -------------------
    if (condition) {
        code A;
    } else {
        code B;
    }
